OL,7,FA gang behind a #6 million investment
OL,8,Fscam that targeted more than 150
OL,9,Fvictims and "hounded" them into
OL,10,Fparting with their savings have been
OL,11,Fjailed.
OL,13,FThe group - five of whom are from
OL,14,FLancashire - targeted mainly elderly
OL,15,Fvictims aged between 60 and 90, using
OL,16,Fwith high-pressure sales tactics to
OL,17,Fpush them into handing over money -
OL,18,Feven convincing one to give #250,000.
