OL,3,CGang jailed for #6 million investment
OL,4,Cscam that targeted more than 150
OL,5,Cvictims
OL,7,FOne victim said he had been left "very
OL,8,Fdepressed with a general loss of faith
OL,9,Fin humanity" following what police
OL,10,Fcalled a crime "of pure greed".
OL,12,FThe gang - jailed for a total of 17
OL,13,Fyears between them - befriended some
OL,14,Fof those they scammed, forging
OL,15,Fdocuments and impersonating insurance
OL,16,Fbrokers in order to steal cash.
OL,18,FMastermind David Clarkson, 70, was
OL,19,Fjailed at Southwark Crown Court on
OL,20,FTuesday 22 July after admitting his
OL,21,Fcrimes at an earlier hearing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
