OL,5,Cvictims
OL,7,FThe remaining defendants were found
OL,8,Fguilty in March after a six-month
OL,9,Ftrial and were also sentenced on
OL,10,FTuesday.
OL,12,FThe court heard City of London Police
OL,13,Fand bank staff managed to recover more
OL,14,Fthan #2 million of the stolen money.
OL,16,FLillian Milner bought herself a
OL,17,FPorsche while many unsuspecting
OL,18,Felderly victims lost their life
OL,19,Fsavings.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
