OL,7,FOne victim said in his impact
OL,8,Fstatement: "I have found it
OL,9,Fincreasingly harder to face the day
OL,10,Fand rarely have a good night's sleep
OL,11,Fwith difficulty finding the motivation
OL,12,Fto get on with the daily tasks at hand.
OL,14,F"Dealing with this case has been very
OL,15,Foverwhelming and mentally consuming,
OL,16,Foften leaving me feeling very
OL,17,Fdepressed with a general loss of faith
OL,18,Fin humanity."
OL,20,FWho was jailed?
