OL,7,FDetective Constable Jay Smith from
OL,8,FCity of London Police said: "These
OL,9,Ffraudsters stole life savings from
OL,10,Fhundreds, abusing their trusted
OL,11,Fpositions out of pure greed.
OL,13,F"Clarkson, in particular, showed no
OL,14,Fremorse ` cloning a regulated insurer
OL,15,Fand impersonating the broker to trick
OL,16,Fvictims and later forging medical
OL,17,Fdocuments to avoid trial.
OL,19,F"Faced with overwhelming evidence, he
OL,20,Feventually pleaded guilty.
