OL,7,F"I thank the victims and their
OL,8,Ffamilies for their strength and co-
OL,9,Foperation, and we remember those who
OL,10,Fsadly passed during the process. I
OL,11,Fhope this result brings some comfort.
OL,13,F"We remain committed to pursuing those
OL,14,Fwho abuse trust and exploit the
OL,15,Fvulnerable. Let this case be a
OL,16,Fwarning: you will be found, prosecuted
OL,17,Fand convicted."
