OL,4,Cscam that targeted more than 150
OL,5,Cvictims
OL,7,FThe police investigation was launched
OL,8,Fwhen suspicious payments were made by
OL,9,Fa company called Sable Intl Ltd to a
OL,10,Fnewly formed law firm in August 2016.
OL,12,FSable claimed to invest in property,
OL,13,Fand opened a #3.5 million bond scheme
OL,14,Foffering fake returns of 7% to lure in
OL,15,Fvictims.
OL,17,FPolice found that the trio behind the
OL,18,Fcompany, David Clarkson, Lillian
OL,19,FMilner and Flaton, had links to an
OL,20,Fearlier investment scheme called
OL,21,FEquitable Law Capital (ELC).
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
