OL,3,CGang jailed for #6 million investment
OL,4,Cscam that targeted more than 150
OL,5,Cvictims
OL,7,FIn reality, none of the investments
OL,8,Fwas genuine, with the trio using
OL,9,Finternet advertising, cold calling and
OL,10,Fcompany brochures to convince victims.
OL,12,FGraham Milner and Paul Clarkson were
OL,13,Fappointed group directors of ELC when
OL,14,Fthey had no relevant experience, and
OL,15,Fbecame involved in money laundering.
OL,17,FA front company based in the
OL,18,FSeychelles and Switzerland was used to
OL,19,Fdisguise the fact the money had come
OL,20,Ffrom crime.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
