OL,7,FLillian Milner and Fallon, who was a
OL,8,Fsolicitor, also used a newly set up
OL,9,Flaw firm to launder money, with
OL,10,Fcommission payments to Flaton going
OL,11,Fthrough an account in Mauritius.
OL,13,FBoth ELC and Sable went into
OL,14,Fadministration and voluntary
OL,15,Fliquidation at the end of 2016, owing
OL,16,Fa total of more than #4 million.
